# FILE: home/about/bio.desc
# ROLE: Global Platform Identity & Educational Philosophy
# ROUTE: /about
# ACCOUNT: All — no auth required
# THEME: Dark · ecosystem visualization · Arabic philosophy

## 1. PAGE HEADER
- section-label "من نحن" + h1 gradient-text "منظومة حلب الأكاديمية"
- Subtitle: tagline about the platform mission
- dot-bg + indigo/teal layered glows

## 2. ECOSYSTEM MAP (Interactive HUD)
- SVG or React-drawn diagram of the 4 platform pillars as nodes
- NODES: [المكتبة] [الأكاديمية] [المستقلون] [المتجر]
- CONNECTIONS: visual data lines between nodes showing inter-platform flow
- HOVER: glassmorphism tooltips explaining each node's benefit
- STYLE: node circles with gradient-bg fill + labeled with emoji + title

## 3. SYSTEM PURPOSE (Philosophy Section)
- HEADER: "تجربة أكاديمية بلا حدود" — gradient-text
- BODY: two paragraphs explaining the platform mission in Arabic
  - Access philosophy
  - Free trial / open access for new users
  - Empowerment of Syrian university students
- STYLE: text-[#94A3B8] · leading-relaxed · max-w-2xl · mx-auto · text-center

## 4. CHALLENGE EVERY DAY SECTION
- Large quote block: italic gradient-text "Challenge Every Day."
- Short explanation of the platform's competitive philosophy
- Subtle pulse animation on the quote mark

## 5. TEAM / ORIGIN NOTE
- Simple card or text section about the platform's origins
- University of Aleppo connection
- No personal names — platform-centric framing

## 6. THREE ACCOUNT TYPES EXPLAINED (Simple Cards)
- 3 cards explaining the ecosystem to new visitors:
  - 🎓 طالب: تعلّم، تصفح، اشترِ، وانضم لسوق المستقلين
  - 💼 أعمال: سوّق منتجاتك، أعلن، أو قدّم خدماتك المهنية
  - 🔐 الإدارة: تُشرف على كل شيء داخل المنظومة

## 7. TYPOGRAPHY
- Font: IBM Plex Sans Arabic · Body: font-light leading-relaxed · Headers: font-black
- Direction: RTL by default
